==English==

===Pronunciation===
*glī'də(r), /ˈɡlaɪdə(r)/, /<tt>"glaId@(r)</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aɪdə(r)|Rhymes: -aɪdə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# An aircraft with fixed wings but no engine, propelled by air currents alone.
# (''mathematics, [[game of life]]'') A configuration which recurs periodically, each time at a fixed offset from the last appearance.

